des:
Get access to the current rankings from the world of sports. This skill will open up a wide range of helpful request about the current standings in golf sport.

Currently you only will have access to the current FedEx standings with this skill. We are working on a way to request the rankings from other tours aswell.

For more information about this skill and our service visit us at https://www.i-like.golf - a beauty of sport!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
